description:
A Day Out adds the following puzzle packs to Puzzle Mode.
The Movies		12 puzzles of sizes 29x20 to 76x44
The Circus		12 puzzles of sizes 24x32 to 43x49
Hobbies			12 puzzles of sizes 34x37 to 50x44
Sports			12 puzzles of sizes 32x32
Themepark		25 puzzles of sizes 24x24 to 60x40
Sightseeing		12 puzzles of 43x75 to 60x100
name: Piczle Lines 2 A Day Out
